      <num>SEC. 2.174</num>
      <heading>Nonapplicability</heading>
      <content>
        <p>The limitations of this division shall not apply to expenditures of a candidate's
               personal funds on behalf of their own candidacy.</p>
        <p>(Ord. No. 5.22, § 6, 4/26/22.)</p>
      </content>
    </section>
